{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@preconcurrency","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"compactMap","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"ElementOfResult","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transform","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@Sendable","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.apple.Swift\/documentation\/Swift\/AsyncSequence\/Element","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sci7ElementQa","text":"Element","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"async","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sci12_ConcurrencyE10compactMapyAA020AsyncThrowingCompactC8SequenceVyxqd__Gqd__Sg7ElementQzYaKclF0H8OfResultL_qd__mfp","text":"ElementOfResult","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?) -> ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.apple.Swift\/documentation\/Swift\/AsyncThrowingCompactMapSequence","preciseIdentifier":"s:12_Concurrency31AsyncThrowingCompactMapSequenceV","text":"AsyncThrowingCompactMapSequence","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"Self","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sci12_ConcurrencyE10compactMapyAA020AsyncThrowingCompactC8SequenceVyxqd__Gqd__Sg7ElementQzYaKclF0H8OfResultL_qd__mfp","text":"ElementOfResult","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":">","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An error-throwing mapping closure. ","type":"text"},{"code":"transform","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"accepts an element of this sequence as its parameter and returns a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"transformed value of the same or of a different type. If ","type":"text"},{"code":"transform","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"throws an error, the sequence ends.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"transform"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An asynchronous sequence that contains, in order, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"non-"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" elements produced by the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transform"},{"type":"text","text":" closure. The sequence"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"ends either when the base sequence ends or when "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transform"},{"type":"text","text":" throws an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"error."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"compactMap(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" method to transform every element received from"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a base asynchronous sequence, while also discarding any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"from the closure. Typically, you use this to transform from one type of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"element to another."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In this example, an asynchronous sequence called "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Counter"},{"type":"text","text":" produces "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Int"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"1"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"5"},{"type":"text","text":". The closure provided to the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"compactMap(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method takes each "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Int"},{"type":"text","text":" and looks up a corresponding "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"String"},{"type":"text","text":" from a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"romanNumeralDict"},{"type":"text","text":" dictionary. Since there is no key for "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"4"},{"type":"text","text":", the closure"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"returns "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" in this case, which "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"compactMap(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" omits from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transformed asynchronous sequence. When the value is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"5"},{"type":"text","text":", the closure"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"throws "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MyError"},{"type":"text","text":", terminating the sequence."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let romanNumeralDict: [Int: String] =","    [1: \"I\", 2: \"II\", 3: \"III\", 5: \"V\"]","","do {","    let stream = Counter(howHigh: 5)","        .compactMap { (value) throws -> String? in","            if value == 5 {","                throw MyError()","            }","            return romanNumeralDict[value]","        }","    for try await numeral in stream {","        print(numeral, terminator: \" \")","    }","} catch {","    print(\"Error: \\(error)\")","}","\/\/ Prints \"I II III Error: MyError() \""]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:Sci12_ConcurrencyE10compactMapyAA020AsyncThrowingCompactC8SequenceVyxqd__Gqd__Sg7ElementQzYaKclF::SYNTHESIZED::s:12_Concurrency28AsyncThrowingFlatMapSequenceV","title":"compactMap(_:)","platforms":[{"name":"iOS","intro